name: Dragon Quest VI - Realms of Revelation [NDS]
description:
Dragon Quest 6: Realms of Revelation is a RPG game developed by ArtePiazza. It came out on 09-12-1995. It was published by Square Enix. Most rawgers rated the game as "Recommended".
You can play Dragon Quest 6: Realms of Revelation on Nintendo DS and SNES.
